Second Department,

September, 1947.

(September 22, 1947.) The People of the State of New York ex rel. Ralph Tropiano, Relator, against Warden of the Civil Prison of Kings County et al., Defendants.

Return on writ of habeas corpus. Writ dismissed and the relator remanded to the custody of the Sheriff of the City of New York. Present — Lewis, P. J., Carswell, Johnston, Nolan and Sneed. JJ.
